Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.10,0:00:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 说什么"暂且就在这里让头脑冷静一下"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.34,0:00:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反正现在就算被丢在这里也不会手足无措了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}炼金术也禁止使用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就和那时的修炼一样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}师父不会认为我们一点都没长进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.43,0:00:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 阿尔 爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别太慌 会掉下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.03,0:00:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们打算干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打算干什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么"啊"呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.98,0:00:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}突然把两人扔在无人岛 我不明白你们的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这么问我也……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:00:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 到底在想什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.27,0:01:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偶尔这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偶尔停下脚步 好好思考一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.77,0:01:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对于现在的他们来说是很必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.13,0:01:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人没有什么牺牲的话就什么都得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.79,0:01:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了得到什么东西 就需要付出同等的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.18,0:01:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就是炼金术的等价交换原则
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那时我们坚信那就是世界的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fn华康雅艺体W6\pos(720,760)\3c&HD3CF9C&\fs70}一即全 全即一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咱们逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行呀 我不会游泳的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么说来 我也不会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 我们跟过去不同了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好开心啊 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 好久没有像这样出来旅游了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}旅游?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那还真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 这个拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刀?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为这里是无人岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有电 没有井 没有挡雨的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}猛兽 大概也没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们两个人独自在这个岛上生活一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这期间不准用炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么会这样?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个月后我会来接你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一即全 全即一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个月找不到答案的话 就把你们送回利森普尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:04:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一即全 全即一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在是明白了 不过那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 那个时候完全不知道那说的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一即全 全即一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个大婶 留些莫名其妙的作业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一即全 全即一 是什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}猜谜游戏吗 根本不明白嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是一个月想不出答案的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正式修炼就泡汤了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 这哪是什么炼金术修炼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被那个老太婆骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}睡吧 明天早起去找吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔 去厕所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}干嘛呀 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}厕所的话 你一个人去就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笨蛋 快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:06:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从这儿逃走的话修炼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么回事呀 千万不要迷了路啊 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的肉可不好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 是我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔 太好了 还以为和你走散了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有两只
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚饭解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好好把身体弄干了 不然会生锈的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个家伙是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可怕 太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明说这儿没有猛兽的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可却有比猛兽更要命的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反正她一个月后才来接咱们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总之 饿着肚子是没法战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有吃的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没想到随便布的陷阱也能捕到猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:09:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要怎么吃呢 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}唰地一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}唰地一下?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是你来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要啊 还是哥哥来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我从来没有杀过动物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太狡猾了 总把不好的事塞给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要紧吧 伤得很重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那只臭狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跑哪儿去了 那混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有小狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肉就算了 还是去吃鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道狐狸能不能吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沉住气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.36,0:11:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚饭 开饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行了 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么"这是什么"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算你饿了 也不能吃得这么难看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是 这里有手印
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看清楚了 这是右手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然有什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你说有什么 难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也许师父带我们来这里就是为了那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:12:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 你要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去调查一下 顺便找点吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们绝对不会放弃的 还有28天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们是为了什么来这里的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们要是死在这里会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}温莉和婆婆会伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我还有很多想做的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种事跟炼金术到底有什么关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想回去…那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找到哥哥的食物了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 快来看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥? 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你叫我啦? 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 刚才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蝉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死掉了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死掉的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放开阿尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.84,0:16:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把阿尔…放开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们曾经谈过要是死在这里会怎样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说是大家会伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个…只是主观的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}客观地来看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使我们死去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}世界也会若无其事地运转
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们的存在真是微不足道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不许说我小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个小小的我死后 肉体会留下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}水 碳 氨 还有石灰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}磷 硝石 盐 硫 镁 氟 锰 还有铝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们的肉体不过是由这些元素\N和几种元素组成的化合物构成的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}终究是要被细菌分解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成为植物的养料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过 那些植物养活了食草动物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}食草动物又养活了食肉动物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在我们不经意间自然而然地循环不息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}眼睛看不到的洪流
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然我不知该把它称作宇宙还是世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我和阿尔都是那洪流中小小的一滴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是"全"中之"一"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过 正是因为有了"一"的聚集 "全"才得以存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这世界依循一种无法想象的巨大法则运转
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}理解这种运转 将其分解并重新构成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第30天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早饭解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到约定的日子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把一即全 全即一的解答告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全是世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很好 进入正式修炼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.03,0:19:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结果还是不在啊 那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知怎的我觉得好像明白了师父说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那时 我们探求到那个答案
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 仅仅那个是不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:20:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实那时应该发现 炼成妈妈是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说不定 我们正要做的事情也全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些事师父一定也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想起来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}意识到了么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个…师父想说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}的确我们曾试图炼成妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结果就是我们现在的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是正因为如此我们才想要取回一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们想把因错误失去的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再用错误挽回吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也许这是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.74,0:21:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 那样的话 要怎样做才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们要前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我们活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.57,0:21:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是你们的决定么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有谁在那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这岛上不是以前就有一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.11,0:21:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定是那时那个戴面具的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为那个人就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咋回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想你们万一出什么事就糟了 所以让他去看着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.23,0:21:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像现在不是说这个的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.07,0:23:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第二十九集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.47,0:23:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无邪的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.83,0:23:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.05,0:23:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他肩上的旧伤…
